WEBVTT

00:00:00.809 --> 00:00:01.960
Prije nekoliko godina,

00:00:01.984 --> 00:00:05.444
dobio sam jedan od onih spam emailova.

00:00:05.468 --> 00:00:07.572
Uspio se probiti kroz moj spam filter.

00:00:07.596 --> 00:00:10.152
Ne znam točno kako, ali
pojavio se u mom inboxu,

00:00:10.176 --> 00:00:12.325
a poslao ga je tip koji se zove
Solomon Odonkoh.

00:00:12.349 --> 00:00:13.564
(Smijeh)

00:00:14.159 --> 00:00:15.310
Znam.

00:00:15.334 --> 00:00:16.564
(Smijeh)

00:00:16.588 --> 00:00:17.748
Ovako je pisalo:

00:00:17.772 --> 00:00:19.390
"Bok, James Veitch,

00:00:19.414 --> 00:00:22.953
Imam zanimljiv poslovni prijedlog
koji želim podijeliti s tobom. Solomon."

00:00:24.246 --> 00:00:27.159
Ruka mi je bila nad tipkom delete.

00:00:27.183 --> 00:00:30.142
Gledao sam u svoj mobitel i razmišljao
kako bih to mogao jednostavno izbrisati.